Flow-1

Flow 1:
buyer selects more than 1 items into the cart, uses the same delivery address, checks out, makes payment & places order which is auto-accepted by seller;
seller fulfills order & sends order & fulfillment state update thru unsolicited /on_status;
buyer selects 1 item for return, seller approves and sends updated quote;
buyer app calculates & updates refund amt for buyer;
